  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is to demonstrate the safety, tolerability, pharmakokinetic and pharmacodynamic
      effect of BAY63-2521 in patients with pulmonary hypertension and stable treatment of
      sildenafil 20 mg.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
